{"title":"光荣伟大十周年","authors":["萧三"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":10,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣伟大十周年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萧三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方红，太阳升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席来到天安门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门，放光芒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片汪洋大沸腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广场万树旌旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片红林生波涛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百年英雄形象在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪念丰碑比天高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿五千万颗心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐飞上天安门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐围绕毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万众欢呼祝国庆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晴空万里乌云散。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日当中光灿烂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请识庐山真面目——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚持光辉总路线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多快好省鼓干劲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进跃进再跃进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓扫一穷和二白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亿万男女一条心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社似朝阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五亿农民喜洋洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里风光无限好："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡村日日换新装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"降龙伏虎歼旱魃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千军万马擒龙王。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从今不靠天吃饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民自己当玉皇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢城处处火龙翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决心赶过老约翰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约翰骑牛我骑马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶他何用十多年？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢煤粮棉四弟兄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并肩携手打冲锋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"移山倒海寻常事。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"复地翻天气概雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五年计划第二轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们两年就完成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改变普通日历者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——毛泽东时代的中国人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方红，太阳升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席来到天安门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他向人民频挥手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广场一片汪洋大沸腾！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}